Seeing Mr. Wright direct.  He is a 41-year-old gentleman who was found to have a large rectal cancer that was obviously a T3 on the outside CT-scan.  It looks to be fairly aggressive with several enlarged lymph nodes in the perirectal region.  He has received preoperative chemoradiation and comes to TR for surgery.

